divs: Sighting DetailsTonight between 6:15 and 7:30 i filmed three different cylinder shaped objects that were flying in a zig zag pattern.I followed them for a while until they disappeared.We continue to see unusual objects in the sky on a weekly basis.They appear out of nowhere darting around disappearing and reappearing,Zig zagging and such.
Summary: Spotted three objects that were cylinder shaped zig zagging through the sky.
